<p>The designer <a href="https://uxplanet.org/@4Barel">Avi Barel</a> made a list of several tools/Free software and other freeware for people who work with design and want to maintain quality with more confidence and even less cost. And he described a little of each one informing which Adobe tool is comparable and we decided to add some information to improve the understanding of such.</p>

<hr />

