<h1 id="in-summary">In summary</h1>

<p>Finally, when it comes to free and open source software, it is so nice to see that there are so many designers involved. You can let us know in the comments about which free and open source product you use as an alternative to any commercial product. Via <a href="https://uxplanet.org/open-design-freeware-tools-for-designers-f7bdde99f2e0">UX Planet</a>, Originally published by Avi Barel on <a href="http://www.startux.net/open-design-freeware-tools-for-designers/">StartUX</a> on February 7, 2018.</p>
